December 19, 2016 at 5:26 PM 路

Estan invitados a nuestra junta el 12/20/16 a las 5:00 donde tendremos La Red Fronteriza que hablara sobre los derechos de los inmigrantes en los Estados Unidos. Tambien se hablara sobrelos servicios del idioma ingles para los estudiantes y por ultimo, tendremos vacunas de la influenza (flu) gratuitas para toda la familia.

You are invited to an event on Tuesday, December 20th at 5:00 pm at La Academia Dolores Huerta. The Border Network for Human Rights will be discussing immigrant rights under the US Constitution. Mrs. Pettes will be explaining the English Language Support Services that are available at LADH for the students who qualify. Ms. Beatriz Vela with the Dept. of Health will be offering flu shots to students, parents, and family members beginning at 4:30. No insurance is required.

Queridos padres del octavo grado,
Estaremos teniendo una junta el pr贸ximo martes, 18 de octubre, a las 5:00 p.m. para platicar sobre importantes temas relacionado con los estudiantes del 8 grado. Esto incluye transici贸n a la preparatoria, planes del siguiente paso, planes de graduaci贸n, el viaje de estudiantes, y la importancia de leer en casa. Tambi茅n esperamos contestar dudas o preguntas. Dear 8th grade parents,

We will be having a meeting next Tuesday, October 18th, at 5:00 p.m. to discuss important issues regarding all 8th grade students. These will include high school transition, next step plans, graduation plans, 8th grade trip, and the importance of having your student continue to read at home. We hope to also answer any questions you might have. We look forward to seeing you there.
Thank you
Socorro Soriano
Octavio Casillas
